			<div class="synopsis">
				<p>Bruce was born and raised in the outskirts of Boston, Mass, moving to South Florida in his early teens.  He still resides there with his wife of 34 years, and his two lovable Malamutes.</p>
				<p>Shortly after starting his first novel, 'The Alien's Gift,' Bruce took vacation to write because the characters in his head insisted on having their story told.  Today he is retired and is fortunate to have the time to write whenever the muse strikes.</p>  
				<p>A long-time lover of sci-fi and science, Bruce also enjoys staying informed of the latest discoveries in the sciences, especially the mind-blowing world of theoretical physics.  Bruce believes that in order to write good sci-fi, you must be grounded in good science.</p>
